import { Component } from '@angular/core'; interface Region { name: string; total: string; establishments: Establishment[]; } interface Establishment { name: string; classes: string; progression: number; percentage: string; } interface Kit { type: string; remaining: number; } interface RealizationEstablishment { name: string; progress: string; progression: number; } interface Activity { name: string; regions: { name: string; total: string; establishments: { name: string; inscriptions: string; }[]; }[]; } @Component({ selector: 'app-dashboard', templateUrl: './dashboard.component.html', styleUrls: ['./dashboard.component.scss'] }) export class DashboardComponent { formations = [ { title: "1ʳᵉ formation des filles - 2ᵉ cycle", regions: [ { name: "COMÈ", total: "51/51", establishments: [ { name: "CEG 2 COMÈ", classes: "16/16", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG 4 COMÈ", classes: "16/16", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG AKODEHA", classes: "19/19", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" } ] }, { name: "BANTÈ", total: "45/45", establishments: [ { name: "CEG 1 BANTÈ", classes: "21/21", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG AKPASSI", classes: "13/13", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG ANOUDE", classes: "11/11", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" } ] }, { name: "HOUÉYOGBÉ", total: "51/51", establishments: [ { name: "CEG HOUÉYOGBÉ", classes: "24/24", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG 1 DOUTOU", classes: "19/19", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG AHOULOUMÈ", classes: "8/8", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" } ] }, { name: "SAVALOU", total: "44/44", establishments: [ { name: "CEG 1 SAVALOU", classes: "24/24", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG 2 SAVALOU", classes: "11/11", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG TCHOGODO", classes: "9/9", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" } ] } ] }, // Ajoutez les autres formations de la même manière ]; sensibilisationData = { title: "Sensibilisation des garçons", regions: [ { name: "COMÈ", total: "51/51", establishments: [ { name: "CEG 2 COMÈ", classes: "16/16", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG 4 COMÈ", classes: "16/16", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" }, { name: "CEG AKODEHA", classes: "19/19", progression: 100, percentage: "100%" } ] }, // ... autres régions ] }; kitsData = { title: "NB DE KITS RESTANTS", regions: [ { name: "BANTÈ", total: "113", warning: true, kits: [ { type: "Kits moyens de 4", remaining: 0 }, { type: "Kits moyens de 2", remaining: 72 }, { type: "Grands kits de 4", remaining: 41 }, { type: "Grands kits de 2", remaining: 0 } ] }, { name: "COMÈ", total: "890", warning: false, kits: [ { type: "Kits moyens de 4", remaining: 100 }, { type: "Kits moyens de 2", remaining: 280 }, { type: "Grands kits de 4", remaining: 310 }, { type: "Grands kits de 2", remaining: 200 } ] }, // ... autres régions ] }; realizationData = { title: "TAUX DE RÉALISATION DES ÉLECTIONS", regions: [ { name: "BANTÈ", total: "28/28", percentage: 100, establishments: [ { name: "CEG 1 BANTÈ", progress: "6/6", progression: 100 }, { name: "CEG AKPASSI", progress: "10/10", progression: 100 }, { name: "CEG ANOUDE", progress: "12/12", progression: 100 } ] }, { name: "COMÈ", total: "10/25", percentage: 40, establishments: [ { name: "CEG 2 COMÈ", progress: "0/3", progression: 0 }, { name: "CEG 4 COMÈ", progress: "10/10", progression: 100 }, { name: "CEG AKODEHA", progress: "0/12", progression: 0 } ] }, // ... autres régions ] }; activitiesData = { title: "NB D'INSCRITS POUR CHAQUE ACTIVITÉ RÉCRÉATIVE", activities: [ { name: "SLAM", regions: [ { name: "BANTÈ", total: "45", establishments: [ { name: "CEG 1 BANTÈ", inscriptions: "21" }, { name: "CEG AKPASSI", inscriptions: "13" }, { name: "CEG ANOUDE", inscriptions: "11" } ] }, // ... autres régions ] }, { name: "ART PLASTIQUE", regions: [ // ... données similaires ] } ] }; getProgressColor(percentage: number): string { if (percentage >= 100) return 'bg-green-500'; if (percentage >= 50) return 'bg-yellow-500'; return 'bg-red-500'; } selectedFormation = this.formations[0]; }
